ynadvancedpayment_itransact_guideline_us:
&#42;&#42;&#42; DO NOT CHANGE HERE &#42;&#42;&#42;
1) To obtain your API Username and API Key you must login into the control panel at https://itransact.com/ -- or, if logged in already, go to "Account settings".

Please check the "REQUIRE API ACCESS FOR XML?" option in the "Fraud Control" section. Then in "Advanced Features" you can get your API Username and API Key.

2) Enable Recurring Billing: This can be enabled via the "Account Settings" link in the Control Panel, enter the URL to be used for postback information. Then select the check-box for recurring. Each time a recurring transaction is processed through our system, our server will post the transaction results to your URL: <b>{postback_url}

3) Please go to https://secure.paymentclearing.com/cgi-bin/rc/recur/recipe_list/list.cgi to add recipe with recipe name format is xdays, xmonths (ex: : 2days, 7days, 1months, ...)
